My skills

As a Product Designer, I participate in many of the design phases, adding value in all of them through my extensive experience, but above all through my analytical skills and attention to detail.

1. Ux/Ui Design

Information Architecture (IA) & User Flows

User Research & Analysis (Interviews, Surveys)

Wireframing, Final design & High-level prototyping

Design Systems & Component Libraries

2. Product Thinking

Product Strategy & Roadmap Planning

Data Analysis (Google Analytics, Adobe Data Collection, etc)

Stakeholder Management & Communication

Agile/Scrum Methodologies

3. Motion Graphics

Micro-interactions & Transitions Design

Principles of Animation (Timing, Easing, etc.)

Storyboarding & Animatic Creation

Lottie/JSON Implementation, RIve & Spline

4. Graphic Design

Visual Identity & Branding

Typography & Color Theory

Iconography & Illustration

Brand storytelling and messaging
